title: Constellation Line
summary: Ships in the Constellation Line are some of the cheapest and fastest ships in the game, sacrificing health and firepower for maneuverability. The unusual playstyles of these ships do allow for unexpected tactics.
full_text:
Constellation Line
Ships in the Constellation Line are some of the cheapest and fastest ships in the game, sacrificing health and firepower for maneuverability. Their low cost makes them very popular among new pilots, and their poor health makes them a laughingstock among experienced pilots. The unusual playstyles of these ships do allow for unexpected tactics.
